Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.90,0:00:13.15,Main,Priestess,0,0,0,,The others should've come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.11,0:00:15.82,Flashback,High elf priestess,0,0,0,,I'll pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.16,0:00:19.16,Flashback,High elf priestess,0,0,0,,Baths feel like the spirits \Nof fire, water, and air
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.16,0:00:22.95,Flashback,High elf priestess,0,0,0,,are all mixed up together. \NThat kind of bugs me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.95,0:00:26.36,Flashback,Dwarf shaman,0,0,0,,We'd much rather have some food and wine.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.36,0:00:30.45,Flashback,Lizardman priest,0,0,0,,I cannot think of anything better \Nfor fatigue than some cheese.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.79,0:00:33.05,Flashback,Priestess,0,0,0,,What about you, Goblin Slayer?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.05,0:00:34.32,Flashback,Goblin slayer,0,0,0,,I'm going to send a letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.74,0:00:36.91,Flashback,Priestess,0,0,0,,A letter?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.91,0:00:37.47,Flashback,Goblin slayer,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.63,0:00:45.12,Main,Priestess,0,0,0,,I really have no idea what he's thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.12,0:00:46.48,Main,Priestess,0,0,0,,I guess that's natural.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.02,0:00:49.82,Main,Priestess,0,0,0,,It's only been a few months since we met.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.66,0:00:59.62,Main,Priestess,0,0,0,,If I hadn't met him...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.58,0:01:02.68,Main,Priestess,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.00,0:01:04.21,Main,Sword Maiden,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.78,0:01:13.94,Main,Sword maiden,0,0,0,,Do you mind if I join you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.18,0:02:49.57,Main,Sword maiden,0,0,0,,I'm sorry for startling you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.35,0:02:52.66,Main,Sword maiden,0,0,0,,My duties kept me a bit late.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.48,0:03:01.12,Main,Priestess,0,0,0,,I-It's fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.64,0:03:05.28,Main,Priestess,0,0,0,,Um... Those scars...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.49,0:03:10.13,Main,Sword maiden,0,0,0,,Oh, these? I made a slight mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.13,0:03:12.77,Main,Sword maiden,0,0,0,,They got me right in the back of the head.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.77,0:03:15.00,Main,Sword maiden,0,0,0,,It happened more than ten years ago, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.13,0:03:17.33,Main,Priestess,0,0,0,,Well, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.80,0:03:21.05,Main,Priestess,0,0,0,,Are you okay now?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.71,0:03:24.32,Main,Sword maiden,0,0,0,,You're a kind person.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.32,0:03:28.93,Main,Sword maiden,0,0,0,,When I tell most people, \Nthey just say, "I'm sorry."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.58,0:03:31.02,Main,Priestess,0,0,0,,But that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.43,0:03:35.57,Main,Sword maiden,0,0,0,,You needn't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.17,0:03:38.86,Main,Sword maiden,0,0,0,,With these eyes,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.80,0:03:42.36,Main,Sword maiden,0,0,0,,I have seen many, many things.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.29,0:03:45.88,Main,Sword maiden,0,0,0,,Things you couldn't even imagine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.88,0:03:50.14,Main,Sword maiden,0,0,0,,That gentleman...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.87,0:03:55.89,Main,Sword maiden,0,0,0,,Goblin Slayer, was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.89,0:03:58.16,Main,Sword maiden,0,0,0,,He seems like quite a dependable fellow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.48,0:04:02.97,Main,Priestess,0,0,0,,Oh, um... Yes, he really is.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.97,0:04:04.93,Main,Sword maiden,0,0,0,,It seems your search is going well.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.94,0:04:10.23,Main,Sword maiden,0,0,0,,But someday...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.57,0:04:13.98,Main,Sword maiden,0,0,0,,I'm sure he will disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.84,0:04:22.49,Main,Priestess,0,0,0,,U-Um, I-I...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.81,0:04:26.24,Main,Sword maiden,0,0,0,,Yes. Make sure you don't stay \Ntoo long, or you may get dizzy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.34,0:04:28.66,Italics,Priestess,0,0,0,,She knows...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.59,0:04:31.95,Italics,Priestess,0,0,0,,She knows
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.11,0:04:34.81,Italics,Priestess,0,0,0,,what the goblins are like.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.62,0:04:42.42,Ep_Title,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fad(274,1)}Onward Unto Death
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.60,0:04:46.65,Main,Adventurer A,0,0,0,,Hey, look. It's a high elf.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.65,0:04:49.55,Main,Adventurer B,0,0,0,,Seriously? I've never seen one before.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.49,0:04:52.96,Main,Adventurer A,0,0,0,,And she's a looker, too. Nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.65,0:04:55.56,Italics,High elf archer,0,0,0,,Well, that's rather unpleasant.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.83,0:04:59.65,Main,High elf archer,0,0,0,,Sorry to keep you waiting. \NSo, did you send your letter?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.65,0:05:00.37,Main,Goblin slayer,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.37,0:05:04.11,Main,Goblin slayer,0,0,0,,There was an adventurer heading to town, \Nso I formally requested that he take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.39,0:05:09.48,Main,High elf archer,0,0,0,,Come to think of it,\NI've never written a letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.48,0:05:12.44,Main,High elf archer,0,0,0,,What do you write in one? \NDo you just report that you're okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.44,0:05:15.21,Main,Goblin slayer,0,0,0,,You're not wrong on the reporting part.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.36,0:05:18.92,Italics,High elf archer,0,0,0,,Which would mean he's sending \Nthem to the farm girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.35,0:05:23.33,Main,High elf archer,0,0,0,,Well, well, Orcbolg, looks like you're \Ncapable of caring about others now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.33,0:05:24.32,Main,Goblin slayer,0,0,0,,Something's wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.32,0:05:26.09,Main,High elf archer,0,0,0,,Wrong? What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.61,0:05:31.35,Main,Goblin slayer,0,0,0,,Despite how large their sewers are, \Nthere isn't a single quest to slay giant rats.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.33,0:05:33.90,Main,Adventurer A,0,0,0,,What a hick.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.90,0:05:36.60,Main,Adventurer B,0,0,0,,Why would those things \Neven exist in this town?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.00,0:05:40.36,Main,High elf archer,0,0,0,,Now that you mention it, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.59,0:05:45.84,Main,High elf archer,0,0,0,,Where are you going, Orcbolg?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.28,0:05:47.78,Main,Goblin slayer,0,0,0,,There's something I need to get.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.24,0:05:50.41,Main,High elf archer,0,0,0,,Ooh, what are you going to buy?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.42,0:05:59.85,Main,High elf archer,0,0,0,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.85,0:06:01.47,Main,Goblin slayer,0,0,0,,You don't know what a bird is?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.47,0:06:03.19,Main,High elf archer,0,0,0,,Of course I do!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.19,0:06:04.13,Main,Goblin slayer,0,0,0,,It's a canary.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.31,0:06:06.48,Main,High elf archer,0,0,0,,I told you, I know what it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.48,0:06:07.41,Main,Goblin slayer,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.87,0:06:14.55,Main,High elf archer,0,0,0,,It's not gonna cause some huge disaster\Nif we touch it, like that scroll, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.55,0:06:17.98,Main,Goblin slayer,0,0,0,,Do you think a canary could kill people?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.98,0:06:21.39,Main,Priestess,0,0,0,,G-Goblin Slayer, that's not what she meant.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.39,0:06:24.23,Main,Priestess,0,0,0,,She's wondering why you brought a canary.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.41,0:06:28.33,Main,Goblin slayer,0,0,0,,When canaries sense even the slightest \Nhint of poison gas, they panic.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.33,0:06:30.37,Main,Priestess,0,0,0,,Poison gas?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.37,0:06:31.14,Main,Goblin slayer,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.58,0:06:35.08,Main,Goblin slayer,0,0,0,,The goblins in the nest \Nhere have been educated.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.80,0:06:39.17,Main,Goblin slayer,0,0,0,,It wouldn't surprise me if they could \Nuse the mechanisms in these ruins.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.17,0:06:43.16,Main,Lizardman priest,0,0,0,,Sir Goblin Slayer, where did \Nyou acquire such knowledge?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.16,0:06:44.27,Main,Goblin slayer,0,0,0,,Miners.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.76,0:06:49.01,Main,Goblin slayer,0,0,0,,Most people in this world have \Nmore knowledge than I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.25,0:06:52.22,Main,Dwarf shaman,0,0,0,,Beard-cutter, where are we headed today?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.61,0:06:54.36,Main,Goblin slayer,0,0,0,,We're going upstream.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.36,0:06:57.53,Main,Goblin slayer,0,0,0,,Their boat came from upstream.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.30,0:06:59.83,Main,Dwarf shaman,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.83,0:07:03.48,Main,Goblin slayer,0,0,0,,We'll do everything we can \Nto avoid running into goblins.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.61,0:07:05.86,Main,HEA,0,0,0,,Wow, that's unusual coming from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.86,0:07:08.28,Main,HEA,0,0,0,,You're actually letting the goblins go?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.39,0:07:10.89,Main,GS,0,0,0,,I'm not letting them go.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.89,0:07:14.18,Main,GS,0,0,0,,I'm going take down their \Nleader and crush them,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.18,0:07:16.25,Main,GS,0,0,0,,then I'll slaughter them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.60,0:07:19.54,Main,P,0,0,0,,Do you think it could be another \Nshaman, or maybe an ogre?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.21,0:07:21.09,Main,GS,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.98,0:07:30.16,Flashback,Sword maiden,0,0,0,,I'm sure he will disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.00,0:07:41.26,Main,LP,0,0,0,,It appears this is where the map ends.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.79,0:07:46.44,Main,HEA,0,0,0,,Th-This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.63,0:07:51.28,Main,GS,0,0,0,,There are traces of soot.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.81,0:07:54.94,Main,HEA,0,0,0,,Does that mean there was a light up there?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.41,0:07:57.53,Main,GS,0,0,0,,A very long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.53,0:08:00.74,Main,GS,0,0,0,,Goblins have very good night \Nvision. They don't use lights.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.96,0:08:07.13,Main,LP,0,0,0,,Warriors or guards... No, it would \Nseem they are adventurers.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.60,0:08:12.22,Main,DS,0,0,0,,I heard there were quite a few \Nbattles in this area back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.79,0:08:17.22,Main,DS,0,0,0,,This painting is probably from \Nfour or five hundred years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.43,0:08:22.97,Main,P,0,0,0,,Oh, could this actually be a grave?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.97,0:08:28.55,Main,P,0,0,0,,For those who had fought on the side \Nof order in the Age of the Gods.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.55,0:08:33.34,Main,HEA,0,0,0,,And now it's just a nest for goblins...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.34,0:08:36.42,Main,HEA,0,0,0,,"Even the brave are at \Nlast brought low," huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.80,0:08:38.87,Main,GS,0,0,0,,That doesn't matter right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.87,0:08:42.57,Main,DS,0,0,0,,You're so impatient, Beard-cutter.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.57,0:08:46.39,Main,DS,0,0,0,,I'm sure the goblins will go \Nrunning when they see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.39,0:08:50.12,Main,GS,0,0,0,,That would be a problem. \NIt'd be a hassle if they ran away.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.00,0:08:53.25,Main,HEA,0,0,0,,The path is getting more complicated.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.25,0:08:57.23,Main,DS,0,0,0,,They must've built it this way so that \Nmonsters wandering in would get confused,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.23,0:08:59.44,Main,DS,0,0,0,,to keep them from disturbing \Nthe dead warriors.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.44,0:09:05.77,Main,DS,0,0,0,,Having to wander around this place as \Na lost spirit would be a cruel fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.77,0:09:09.03,Main,LP,0,0,0,,It would also remove one from \Nthe circle of death and rebirth.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.03,0:09:12.56,Main,LP,0,0,0,,But this place already \Nbelongs to the goblins.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.56,0:09:15.33,Main,LP,0,0,0,,The drawing of the map cannot \Nbe done half-heartedly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.33,0:09:18.20,Main,LP,0,0,0,,We must all remain vigilant.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.38,0:09:22.34,Main,P,0,0,0,,So we're going into this room first?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.34,0:09:26.23,Main,HEA,0,0,0,,It's not locked, and it doesn't \Nlook like there are any traps.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.23,0:09:27.83,Main,HEA,0,0,0,,Not on the door, at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.09,0:09:32.49,Main,HEA,0,0,0,,Also, I'm not an expert at this, so don't \Nget mad at me if things go wron—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.49,0:09:33.30,Main,GS,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.32,0:09:41.76,Main,HEA,0,0,0,,Look, over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.33,0:09:44.81,Main,P,0,0,0,,How awful!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.50,0:09:49.47,Main,P,0,0,0,,Wh-What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.47,0:09:50.26,Main,GS,0,0,0,,Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.28,0:10:07.28,Main,LP,0,0,0,,This is not good. They've locked us in.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.13,0:10:15.16,Main,HEA,0,0,0,,Goblins!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.16,0:10:17.41,Main,DS,0,0,0,,Looks like they got one over on us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.41,0:10:21.93,Main,P,0,0,0,,N-No... G-Goblin Slayer...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.93,0:10:22.81,Main,GS,0,0,0,,Calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.96,0:10:24.83,Main,GS,0,0,0,,We're still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.34,0:10:28.14,Main,HEA,0,0,0,,Poison gas!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.10,0:10:48.29,Main,LP,0,0,0,,This is not good. We're trapped like rats.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.51,0:10:51.31,Main,DS,0,0,0,,The poison gas probably won't kill us,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.31,0:10:53.80,Main,DS,0,0,0,,but it definitely doesn't make things easier.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.80,0:10:56.30,Main,HEA,0,0,0,,It's no use. I can't find another exit.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.35,0:11:01.01,Main,P,0,0,0,,Wh-What should we do, Goblin Slayer?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.01,0:11:04.18,Main,P,0,0,0,,I haven't been granted the \Nmiracle to remove poison yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.18,0:11:08.50,Main,GS,0,0,0,,Wrap this in a piece of cloth, and \Nhold it over your nose and mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.50,0:11:11.08,Main,P,0,0,0,,Is that... charcoal?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.08,0:11:12.65,Main,GS,0,0,0,,It'll protect you from the poison.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.08,0:11:15.39,Main,GS,0,0,0,,If you have any herbs on hand, \Nput those in there, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.84,0:11:17.48,Main,GS,0,0,0,,Be quick, or you'll die.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.99,0:11:24.64,Main,GS,0,0,0,,Those are bags of quicklime and volcanic \Nearth. Mix them up and block the holes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.63,0:11:27.58,Main,DS,0,0,0,,Concrete!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.91,0:11:29.75,Main,GS,0,0,0,,It won't dry immediately, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.75,0:11:33.25,Main,DS,0,0,0,,Don't worry. I've got a weathering spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.81,0:11:37.65,Main,HEA,0,0,0,,I'll go around and block all the holes!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.65,0:11:39.65,Main,HEA,0,0,0,,Dwarf, get going on that spell!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.65,0:11:40.67,Main,DS,0,0,0,,You got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.10,0:11:45.13,Main,DS,0,0,0,,Tick-tock, tick-tock, spin, spin, O Chronos.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.13,0:11:47.34,Main,Ds,0,0,0,,Let the pendulum swing and move again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.66,0:11:49.17,Main,Ds,0,0,0,,Weathering!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.44,0:11:57.32,Main,LP,0,0,0,,Well, well. It appears that Sir Mage \Nhas many tricks up his sleeve.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.32,0:12:01.77,Main,LP,0,0,0,,So, what are you planning to \Ndo next, Sir Goblin Slayer?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.07,0:12:08.13,Main,GS,0,0,0,,We'll move one of these stone coffins \Nin front of the door to block it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.67,0:12:11.61,Main,GS,0,0,0,,Once the poison dissipates, \Nthey're going to barge in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.88,0:12:23.76,Main,LP,0,0,0,,This should take care of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.16,0:12:26.81,Main,HEA,0,0,0,,We've finished plugging all the holes, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.81,0:12:29.87,Main,DS,0,0,0,,That being said, I'm out of spells.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.87,0:12:31.42,Main,GS,0,0,0,,Then take up a weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.37,0:12:40.35,Main,LP,0,0,0,,Shall I summon a dragontooth warrior?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.89,0:12:43.81,Main,P,0,0,0,,I-I'll cast Protection!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.81,0:12:44.78,Main,GS,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.78,0:12:49.57,Main,LP,0,0,0,,O horns and claws of the father, Iguanodon,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.57,0:12:52.47,Main,LP,0,0,0,,be four limbs and walk upon \Nthis earth with two legs...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.74,0:12:52.06,Main,P,0,0,0,,{\an8}O merciful Earth Mother,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.06,0:12:55.83,Main,P,0,0,0,,{\an8}please protect us, the weak, \Nwith the powers of the earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.82,0:12:58.16,Main,LP,0,0,0,,A dragontooth warrior!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.48,0:12:59.29,Main,P,0,0,0,,Protection!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.62,0:13:08.26,Main,HEA,0,0,0,,It's quiet outside now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.61,0:13:12.28,Main,GS,0,0,0,,Since we plugged up the holes, \Nthe poison gas will reverse its flow.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.77,0:13:14.79,Main,GS,0,0,0,,I'm sure at least a few of them died.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.12,0:13:29.42,Main,HEA,0,0,0,,Footsteps...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.42,0:13:32.33,Main,HEA,0,0,0,,I can't tell how many there are, \Nbut something strange is among them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.41,0:13:34.58,Main,DS,0,0,0,,Here they come!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.51,0:13:46.34,Main,GS,0,0,0,,A hob... No...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.58,0:13:50.05,Main,GS,0,0,0,,A goblin champion.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.50,0:13:52.47,Main,GS,0,0,0,,We'll cut our way through.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.47,0:13:55.02,Main,LP,0,0,0,,Indeed. Let my blade assist you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.03,0:14:07.15,Main,P,0,0,0,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.14,0:14:20.06,Main,GS,0,0,0,,Six.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.75,0:14:23.48,Main,GS,0,0,0,,You can go all-out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.48,0:14:24.55,Main,LP,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.40,0:14:36.52,Main,HEA,0,0,0,,Damn it, there's a lot of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.78,0:14:39.28,Main,DS,0,0,0,,No use complaining about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.28,0:14:40.80,Main,DS,0,0,0,,You holdin' up over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.80,0:14:43.32,Main,P,0,0,0,,Some... what...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.65,0:14:45.81,Main,GS,0,0,0,,Seventeen.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.97,0:15:07.42,Main,P,0,0,0,,Goblin Slayer!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.75,0:15:10.30,Main,HEA,0,0,0,,Orcbolg! Did they get him?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.48,0:15:25.46,Main,P,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.30,0:15:28.36,Main,HEA,0,0,0,,The Protection...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.81,0:15:30.50,Main,LP,0,0,0,,How could this be?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.27,0:15:33.20,Main,HEA,0,0,0,,Calm down and concentrate!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.72,0:15:36.12,Main,DS,0,0,0,,Long-ears!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.63,0:15:42.96,Main,DS,0,0,0,,You stupid goblins! Unhand her!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.98,0:15:56.93,Main,P,0,0,0,,N-No...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.44,0:16:28.37,Main,HEA,0,0,0,,Let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.37,0:16:29.67,Main,DS,0,0,0,,Why, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.55,0:16:41.57,Flashback,Guy,0,0,0,,You think you can slay goblins?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.17,0:16:46.22,Flashback,Guy,0,0,0,,You just sat and watched quietly.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.22,0:16:50.35,Flashback,Guy,0,0,0,,You were powerless. You didn't do a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.42,0:16:59.93,Main,GS,0,0,0,,Bullshit.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.91,0:18:10.12,Main,GS,0,0,0,,I heard that assassins like using string \Nmade of human hair as a killing tool.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.94,0:18:14.89,Main,GS,0,0,0,,Apparently it doesn't break \Neasily or come undone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.82,0:18:30.54,Main,HEA,0,0,0,,Go! Hurry up and heal her!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.97,0:18:32.45,Main,LP,0,0,0,,Thank you for the assistance.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.34,0:18:34.58,Main,HEA,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.85,0:18:38.69,Main,HEA,0,0,0,,To think I'd end up owing a dwarf a favor...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.69,0:18:42.46,Main,HEA,0,0,0,,But I'd shame all elves if I didn't thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.46,0:18:46.88,Main,DS,0,0,0,,You were on the verge of tears. \NYou sure have a lot of spunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.88,0:18:48.80,Main,HEA,0,0,0,,At least I have some!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.80,0:18:50.27,Main,HEA,0,0,0,,Orcbolg!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.80,0:18:50.27,Main,DS,0,0,0,,Beard-cutter!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.80,0:18:50.27,Main,LP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Sir Goblin Slayer!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.69,0:18:55.37,Main,HEA,0,0,0,,Kill it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.51,0:18:59.78,Flashback,Guy,0,0,0,,Onward unto death!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.78,0:19:03.41,Flashback,Guy,0,0,0,,Die like a nail hammered into a coffin!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.01,0:19:12.03,Main,GS,0,0,0,,Hey, take a good look, goblin!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.66,0:19:25.03,Main,GS,0,0,0,,Who's next?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.31,0:19:28.52,Main,GS,0,0,0,,Is it you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.81,0:19:33.21,Main,GS,0,0,0,,Or you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.47,0:20:06.86,Main,HEA,0,0,0,,Orcbolg.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.03,0:20:09.19,Main,GS,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.19,0:20:14.17,Main,HEA,0,0,0,,Somewhat. But you're not all right, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.77,0:20:18.82,Main,GS,0,0,0,,Yeah... Where's the girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.82,0:20:20.78,Main,HEA,0,0,0,,Over there. Can you walk?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.20,0:20:22.34,Main,GS,0,0,0,,I'll try...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.40,0:20:28.47,Main,DS,0,0,0,,Up you go. Come on, get a hold of yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.47,0:20:32.53,Main,DS,0,0,0,,We still have to get home.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.53,0:20:33.34,Main,GS,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.65,0:20:41.92,Main,LP,0,0,0,,Bless the stars... Thank goodness \Nwe somehow made it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.29,0:20:43.13,Main,GS,0,0,0,,How is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.70,0:20:45.93,Main,LP,0,0,0,,She will survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.37,0:20:50.68,Main,LP,0,0,0,,Had the wound been any deeper, \Nthere would've been nothing I could do.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.15,0:20:52.16,Main,GS,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.97,0:20:58.90,Main,P,0,0,0,,I'm... sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.64,0:21:04.24,Main,GS,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.46,0:21:10.71,Main,P,0,0,0,,Gob... lin... Slay... er...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.67,0:21:13.64,Main,GS,0,0,0,,These things happen...
